Q2: Identify Suspicious Activities & Generate Report [15 Marks]
Suspicious Activities to Look For
Activity	Indicator	Severity
Brute Force Attack	Multiple failed logins from same IP	🔴 High
Privilege Escalation	New admin account created	🔴 High
Malware Execution	Suspicious processes running	🔴 High
Unauthorized Access	Login at odd hours	🟡 Medium
Data Exfiltration	Large file transfers	🔴 High
Account Misuse	Multiple logins same user	🟡 Medium
System Changes	Firewall/service disabled	🟡 Medium
Common Suspicious Patterns
Pattern	What It Means	Action
10+ failed logins in 1 minute	Brute force attack	Block IP
Login at 3 AM	Possible compromise	Investigate
Unknown process running	Malware	Quarantine
New admin account	Backdoor	Disable account
Firewall disabled	Attack preparation	Enable + investigate
